node.text: Quite frankly, sleep means everything to me😂 I have struggled with finding a mattress that doesn’t make my back pain worse for yearssss. We got an @sleepokioki mattress a few weeks ago, and the difference in the quality of our sleep is unbelievable. I wake up without back pain and Davey doesn’t keep me awake all night with his tossing and turning 🙃we decided on the OkiFirm I cannot recommend it enough! #OkiOkipartner

Good morning, everybody! Today I wanted to share my daily skincare routine with @infinitekparis.us 😊👇🏻

Steps:
1.Dead Sea Mud Mask: improves and prevents the appearance of acne, blackheads, and enlarged pores. 
2. Vitamin C Serum: Improves skin tone and texture.
3. Multi-Active 360: Special for dark circles, eye bags, and puffiness. 
4. Hyaluronic Acid Serum: Provides intense hydration and protection.
5. Sunscreen Ultra Protection SPF 50: 100% mineral formula, protects from the damage caused by UVA, UVB, and Blue Light.
If you stick with this routine you will notice HUGE changes in your skin! @infinitekparis.us

node.text: Our lives are made up of the people that have come and gone, taught us lessons, stayed for the long haul and given us their time and love. I have been dealt a wonderful hand in life and I thank the people that have filled my world with so much happiness the past 28 years. My birthday wish for this next year is to make my loved ones proud and never taking a single minute of this life for granted ❤️
